data.title: Clerks III BluRay - SIGNED by KEVIN, JAY, Brian O'Halloran and Jeff Anderson
data.meta_description: Clock back into the Clerks universe for writer-director Kevin Smith's third entry of his iconic comedy series. Once again behind the counter of Quick Stop, Dante (Brian O'Halloran) and Randal (Jeff Anderson) are still hanging out with Jay and Silent Bob (Jason Mewes, Kevin Smith) handling quirky customers, and sneaking off for rooftop hockey. but after Randal has a heart attack, he's determined to make something of his slacker life - by shooting a movie about it! Featuring Rosario Dawson, a host of celebrity cameos, and Smith signature humor, Clerks III is a hilarious nostalgic capstone to the Clerks legacy - nearly thirty years in the making. Signed by Jason Mewes, Kevin Smith, Brian O'Halloran and Jeff Anderson.
